{"tid":2408686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"信和商場使用「安心出行」可獲20元現金券；新地商場使用則可獲500積分","createTime":"2021-02-15T07:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:56:36.000Z","uid":4007,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da4b419f4078ee7cb0c78b05b1e7012a617c3761","tid":2408686,"uid":4007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"為鼓勵市民安裝「安心出行」流動應用程式，多個商場均送出優惠，繼新地（0016）後，信和（0083）旗下四商場，包括屯門市廣場、奧海城、荃新天地及中港城於即日起，免費送出20元 S現金券予下載及使用「安心出行」流動應用程式的顧客。<br />\n<br />\n信和集團指，由即日起至本月24日， S+ REWARDS會員只要成功下載「安心出行」流動應用程式，並到屯門市廣場、奧海城、荃新天地或中港城掃描場所二維碼，即可到以上商場禮賓處出示該出行記錄，免費換領$20 S現金券，毋須任何消費。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1612957646161&amp;issue=20210210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1612957646161%26issue%3D20210210&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eSF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=47817e29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1612957646161&amp;issue=20210210</a><br />\n<br />\n為響應政府相關抗疫措施，新地（0016）旗下商場設有「安心出行」二維碼，並鼓勵市民使用。由明日起至本月24日，在新地旗下 22 個主要商場使用「安心出行」流動應用程式記錄個人行程後 ，到商場顧客服務中心向職員出示「出行記錄」頁面，毋須任何消費，即可獲得「The Point by SHKP」500 積分。名額不限，唯每人只可獲得獎賞一次。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1612944076100&amp;issue=20210210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1612944076100%26issue%3D20210210&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eSF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=71728c92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1612944076100&amp;issue=20210210</a>"},{"pid":"f54996c240950303292ab48e10897789254a108b","tid":2408686,"uid":212702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832670e7ee3defc7dbac0bc4de1bc40622502bb6","tid":2408686,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T0